data = {"time":1643491331617,"blocks":[{"id":"Thxa5O4lA4","type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"To listen to music together, you must create a group and invite friends to it first. Then, you will be able to create lounges and listen to music together."}},{"id":"2uQUEGda12","type":"checklist","data":{"items":[{"text":"Setup a group","checked":false},{"text":"Create a lounge","checked":false},{"text":"Join a listening party","checked":false},{"text":"Listen together","checked":false}]}},{"id":"LYNAHhvVU5","type":"Header","data":{"text":"Create or Join a Group","level":2}},{"id":"6lWSTImsNa","type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"To create a group, you can click the + on the left side of the Parallel app. You will be shown options to create or join a group.&nbsp;"}},{"id":"ipc1Y5VMWU","type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"If you are creating a group, after creating it, you need to invite your friends by clicking the \"Copy Invite Link\" button in the group header. Other users will use this code to join your group."}},{"id":"V94wIGwRtC","type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"If you are joining a group, paste the invitation code to the input field after selecting \"Join Group\" from the + dropdown."}},{"id":"Ml4CUf_-gA","type":"Header","data":{"text":"Create a Lounge","level":2}},{"id":"OMGz_ZwvnT","type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"To create a lounge, the group owner or a group's staff member can select the + button on the group sidebar. After following the onscreen instructions, users will be able to select the lounge from the sidebar to open it."}},{"id":"jZbNi_V1ZS","type":"image","data":{"url":"data:image/png;base64,","caption":"Example lounge","withBorder":false,"withBackground":true,"stretched":false}},{"id":"dx512r8_4h","type":"Header","data":{"text":"Join a Listening Party","level":2}},{"id":"fMLT0-K4Xa","type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"You can join a listening party separately from a voice call. You can join a listening party by selecting one of the buttons near the bottom-right of the lounge.&nbsp;"}},{"id":"62b__g4zg-","type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"After you and your friends have joined the listening party, the music tab in the lounge will be made available."}},{"id":"qOROsA2T7O","type":"image","data":{"url":"data:image/png;base64,","caption":"This is where you can play or manage tracks.","withBorder":false,"withBackground":false,"stretched":false}},{"id":"b9bEfFPmE0","type":"Header","data":{"text":"Listen Together","level":2}},{"id":"WE46lmAJuo","type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"All connected members will have access to adding tracks to the queue and listening to the tracks being played."}},{"id":"uxwK0WN_Z0","type":"paragraph","data":{"text":"Only the group owner or appointed staff members can access controls like clearing the queue or skipping the current track."}}],"version":"2.22.2","title":"Guide to Group Listening"}; runStart();